summary: I'm a web editor and literary translator with experience in the cultural sector and higher education. I have taught and designed workshops in fields including English and Dutch language acquisition, translation, writing and illustration. I enjoy the challenge of structuring information effectively online and in a classroom setting.  In my free time I like creating graphic short stories, illustrations and other visual work.
